headline: Fair Isaac: Fiscal Q1 Earnings Snapshot
summary: FICO) on Wednesday reported fiscal first-quarter profit of $158.4 million. The Bozeman, Montana-based company said it had profit of $6.61 per share. Earnings, adjusted for one-time gains and costs, were $7.33 per share.

headline: FICO Partners with LoanPASS to Launch First Batch Pricing Tool for FICO® Score 10T
